---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Speaker Rider | Joe Karlsson" description="Joe Karlsson's requirements for speaking at events.">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-8">
		<h1 class="mb-8 text-3xl font-bold text-white">Speaker Rider</h1>
		<div class="prose">
			<p>
				Before I'll agree to a speaking engagement, I research the event
				and its organizers to make sure it aligns with my values. Here are my requirements.
			</p>

			<h2>Requirements</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Code of Conduct</strong> — The event must have a clearly stated and enforced code of conduct.</li>
				<li><strong>Diversity</strong> — The speaker lineup should include speakers from underrepresented groups in tech.</li>
				<li><strong>Travel & Accommodation</strong> — For out-of-town events, I ask that travel and hotel expenses be covered.</li>
				<li><strong>Compensation</strong> — For corporate events, I expect a speaker fee. I'm flexible for community events and non-profits.</li>
				<li><strong>Recording</strong> — I'm happy to have my talk recorded and shared publicly.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>What I Offer</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Engaging, well-prepared technical talks with live demos</li>
				<li>Active promotion of the event on social media</li>
				<li>Availability for Q&A, meet-and-greets, and networking</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				Interested in having me speak? <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
